{"tid":2496523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「8岁反华」成敏感詞","createTime":"2021-04-20T01:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T03:47:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6948eef8e32b562fa46304b86e8ab67375c6916c","tid":2496523,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T01:47:33.000Z","msg":"近日，中共自曝安全機關辦理的多個所謂「反華」典型案例。其中一名學生被控自「8歲」起收聽「反華」廣播，令網友驚愕，網友指他是一位覺醒青年、優秀新聞記者....<br />\n<br />\n據中國數字時代（China Digital Times；CDT）敏感詞週報統計，目前「8歲+反華」已成為級別高的敏感詞。<br />\n<br />\n文章稱，微博對該案觸及細節的討論加以嚴格限制，據微博話題榜數據#境外反華敵對勢力拉攏內地學生內幕#，#央視曝李亨利的漢奸行徑#兩個話題共計有2.4萬討論和1.9億閱讀。但以官方文本中的「8歲+反華」進行搜索發現僅有4個結果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2021/04/id12891175-tcFotoJet-450x300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fid12891175-tcFotoJet-450x300.jpg&h=50d181a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/4/19/n12891142.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F21%2F4%2F19%2Fn12891142.htm&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuCKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=34033fd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/4/19/n12891142.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a0bd604bec0fc80bf082c3f0ed422ced12013b22","tid":2496523,"uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T01:48:38.000Z","msg":"反华（8岁）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0942eb9c373e1fe48bf64f25a58239517820fd34","tid":2496523,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T01:56:23.000Z","msg":"自岀世起就沒有宣誓愛国<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164ef3accbc83afaed215e2cde389b744af0e46f","tid":2496523,"uid":2192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:33:44.000Z","msg":"繁華<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc48d4b58f220685680895a3f54c991258c7c3c","tid":2496523,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:47:30.000Z","msg":"準備完全封牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}